programs.program:
as principal admin password "admin" do
set records = []
append to records with { name = "mike", date = "1-1-90" }
append to records with { name = "michelle", date = "1-1-85" }
append to records with { name = "dave", date = "1-1-85" }
local names = records
filtereach rec in records with let lhs = split(rec.name,"..") in let rhs = split("milosh","..") in equal(lhs.fst,rhs.fst)
filtereach rec in names with let r = { name = "dave", date = "1-1-85" } in equal(rec,r)
append to records with names
return records
***
